<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "4C">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "03">
<configtype typenbr = "1">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B4316003" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Rear Brake Drum Removal and Installation
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4316003001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B4316002">Rear Brake Shoe On-Vehicle Inspection:Drum Brake Model</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hoist vehicle and remove rear wheel. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B2406001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Release parking brake.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove rear brake drum (2) by screwing M8 bolts (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P431002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.310mm" ver = "01" gw = "114" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4316003002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B4316004">Rear Brake Drum and Shoe Inspection:Drum Brake Model</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
To maximize brake shoe-to-drum clearance, put screwdriver between rod (1) and ratchet (2) and push down ratchet as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B431002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.109mm" ver = "01" gw = "175" gh = "131"/>
</figure>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
The figure below shows the ratchet position where brake shoe-to-drum clearance is maximum.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01430009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "191" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.038in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.038in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Rod
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ratchet
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that inside of rear brake drum and rear brake shoes are free from dirt and oil.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Adjust parking brake cable referring to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4406002">Parking Brake Inspection and Adjustment</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install rear wheel referring to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B2406001">Wheel (with Tire) Removal and Installation</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that brake drum does not drag and brake provides proper braking. Perform brake test (foot brake and parking brake).
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
